{"word":"G2306 - θειώδης - theiṓdēs - thi-o'-dace - Brimstone","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θειώδης</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">theiṓdēs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">thi-o'-dace</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Brimstone</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கந்தகம் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"of brimstone, sulphurous"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2303 - θεῖον - theîon - thi'-on/2303\">G2303</a> and <a href=\"#/G1491 - εἶδος - eîdos - i'-dos/1491\">G1491</a>; <i>sulphur like</i>, that is, <i>sulphurous:</i> - brimstone.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}